<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. A bei huoi huoi ie I damlai niuhaw hi
 I kipahnau muol a liem kit sek
 Vaihkit gawleu a kilawm puoi
 Ngai in thil mah leng le.

[V2]
 Lungdeih len-guol ngaihte kikhen tadih mah leng
 Lawp leh nuomin lungguol takin;
 Damlai lam suk leh to ahin
 I Lalpau na chu sem hitiu.

[V3]
 2. Zan thim nuoi leh sun lunghelna ahin le,
 Lei gim theihna hin ei chawkbuoi sek;
 I lungkham nau kipah suok hen,
 A kaplai hai hitiu.

[V4]
 3. Lalpa, ei kai in Aw len-guol deih cheng tawh
 Na lenna zaila tawh zuon thei din
 Kikhen na him lau ta puong kau
 Lungkham buoina khelah.

[V5]
 4. Mitthi thieka kikhenna a lau ta puou
 Aksi khel gam nuoma lengte khun
 Zaila a sau gihawih cheng tawh
 Lopina gam nuomah.</lyrics>
<title>A Bei Huoi Huoi Ie !</title>
<author>Thangngur</author>
<hymn_number>278</hymn_number>
</song>